### Flow 1: Q&A — product question
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Tell me about laptops, what do you have?",
  "session_id": "qa-demo"
}

### Flow 1: Q&A — follow-up, same session
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Do you have any wireless headphones?",
  "session_id": "qa-demo"
}

### Flow 2: Order — HITL step 1: draft
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to buy a ProBook 15",
  "session_id": "order-demo"
}

### Flow 2: Order — HITL step 2: confirm
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "yes",
  "session_id": "order-demo"
}

### Flow 2 (variant): Order — HITL step 1: draft
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "I want to buy BudgetPhone X",
  "session_id": "order-cancel-demo"
}

### Flow 2 (variant): Order — HITL step 2: cancel
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "no",
  "session_id": "order-cancel-demo"
}

### Guardrail: off-topic — should be rejected
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What's the weather like today?",
  "session_id": "guard-demo"
}

### Guardrail: empty message — Pydantic 422
POST {{host}}/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "",
  "session_id": "guard-demo"
}
